Hybrid Playwright framework:
•	Playwright Test Runner
•	Cucumber BDD
•	POM with proper OOPS
•	Data-driven
•	Fixtures + modular helpers
•	Thin root config (Option-1)
•	Target app: Zero Bank (zero.webappsecurity.com)
•	Pages covered: Home, Login, Feedback
No shortcuts, no pseudo-code, no missing references.
